            "title": "生日會氫氣球碰到蠟燭爆炸！ 女子半邊臉灼傷冒煙｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/a0a7bfeaf03071efbfd54177d1c10102/0274748d7742446c9e27421ddf6534e3-2f60eff2450abef6d92e7a83e9235285-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b8478ba3afa\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67b8478ba3afd\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"生日會氫氣球碰到蠟燭爆炸！ 女子半邊臉灼傷冒煙\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c1a44e06fa0731536d1320c1af0ed292/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250221/_2025022117274940952.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">生日會氫氣球碰到蠟燭爆炸！ 女子半邊臉灼傷冒煙</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>越南河內發生一宗駭人意外，一名女子慶祝生日時開心捧着蛋糕拍照時，手上的氣球意外碰到蛋蠟上的蠟燭，瞬間發生猛烈氣爆，火焰直衝天花。女子半邊臉灼傷，甚至邊逃跑邊冒煙，驚悚畫面在網路上曝光。\n\n</p><h2>火焰直衝天花場面驚悚</h2>\n<p>這名女子20日在facebook公開自己的傷勢照，只見她的右臉嚴重燒燙傷，嘴唇、脖子及右前臂等部位也受波及，所幸經過治療後，傷口妥善包紮後情況穩定。她報平安說皮膚正逐漸恢復中。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"事發時女子正準備吹蠟燭慶生。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4873066da445ea05e7cf259862798e9f/2025-02/Image1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事發時女子正準備吹蠟燭慶生。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"她一手拿氣球一手拿蛋糕，身體隨音樂擺動。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/80d385ddfc12a0cb820c66ff6269aa66/2025-02/Image2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        她一手拿氣球一手拿蛋糕，身體隨音樂擺動。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"豈料氣球飄動時，剛好碰上蠟燭。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a55f29905e49b4b296d47000dd8e51ab/2025-02/Image3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        豈料氣球飄動時，剛好碰上蠟燭。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"氣球隨即爆炸。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/704f7725f79cdc32374ed21a8c01a8f9/2025-02/Image4_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        氣球隨即爆炸。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"炸出大團火焰。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3757a35039229e43fe5e9120b7160dd7/2025-02/Image5_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        炸出大團火焰。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火焰往上升。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a0cfaea1ba94581167180b90cb17086e/2025-02/Image6_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火焰往上升。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火焰直衝天花板。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/070443e20200e679cc35e6698c2e9bc0/2025-02/Image7_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火焰直衝天花板。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火勢瞬間熄滅，女子低頭逃走。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9b783bb574d61986937d7019a0b8f5a9/2025-02/Image8_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火勢瞬間熄滅，女子低頭逃走。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"從片中可見她一邊走一邊臉上冒煙。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4f398ae11839f1adfb72b770ad94d6e/2025-02/Image9_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        從片中可見她一邊走一邊臉上冒煙。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"事主臉部及右臂灼傷。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6d6415fb89c9a7164b9e0296495ad022/2025-02/480643156_1044133361088000_2189966286634965036_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事主臉部及右臂灼傷。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"所幸經處理後無大礙，事主表示皮膚正在康復。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d5ec83437a0191a516de973c42daa022/2025-02/480810420_1153187266177961_1206692789815464847_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        所幸經處理後無大礙，事主表示皮膚正在康復。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"事主半邊臉灼傷。 facebook\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e59f071d27a44f120f32ab4ee282183a/2025-02/480984755_2888821931277856_1155982887064946907_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        事主半邊臉灼傷。 facebook\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3415714/\">除夕倒數｜河南氫氣球連鎖爆燃 數人被灼傷｜有片</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>從曝光的畫面可以看到，事發時女子一手拿氣球，一手捧蛋糕，在音樂襯托下輕鬆搖擺着身體，氣球也跟着飄。豈料其中一個大型氫氣球碰到蛋糕上的蠟燭，現場瞬間發生爆炸，猛烈火光直竄天花板。牆上的一排氣球也被點燃，像燒炮仗般噼啪作響。女子下意識掩面逃走，可見她一邊走臉上一邊冒煙。\n\n</p>\n<p>女子事後決定公開影片，提醒大家氫氣球的潛在危險，希望藉由自身經歷，讓更多人提高警覺，避免發生類似意外。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
